{"tid":163900,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[委屈]係香港食煙真係好慘","createTime":"2017-03-20T10:12:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-01T15:38:42.000Z","uid":5649,"like":34,"dislike":593,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"44cda660891ce3f0f73e3239ebb20ee1a384971c","tid":163900,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:12:12.000Z","msg":"煙價成日加<br />\n食煙既地方越黎越少（茶餐廳都唔比食）<br />\n無地方食，咁有時影響到人好正常，又比人啤<br />\n有無平權撚可以幫下我地煙民發聲"},{"pid":"fce11efd5d1240b331c230305b446d598558a289","tid":163900,"uid":35754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:14:33.000Z","msg":"留喺屋企食唔撚得？"},{"pid":"4aa30f319c2e845f009ec08f100b74dcc78654f2","tid":163900,"uid":80630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:15:36.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過d唔食煙既焗住要吸你地噴出黎既毒氣啊<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b02ceea42c7e4e8e378e539ce2462cefe9783b8e","tid":163900,"uid":1314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:15:57.000Z","msg":"你都識講影響到人好正常"},{"pid":"14adc65f4af7776bf069d758410c7621a270c6c7","tid":163900,"uid":3974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:19:04.000Z","msg":"唔理咁多啦<br />\n整枝先<br />\n（點煙+派🚬）"},{"pid":"3e97382419dfd9484f86e132d1cc686e977dd7dc","tid":163900,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:19:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你都識講影響到人好正常</blockquote><br />\n係呀唔知有咩問題，無啦啦比人啤"},{"pid":"fc47a6c7d3b0dbdcdff6a5d7c47bbce584075600","tid":163900,"uid":74918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:22:03.000Z","msg":"好撚憎D人邊行邊食 <br />\n完全唔諗下其他人唔撚想吸D2手煙既<br />\n最好全港公眾地方禁煙"},{"pid":"784617d95384f3d169734fc8415b0971cccb61a1","tid":163900,"uid":29275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:22:27.000Z","msg":"巴打，既然食煙食到咁谷氣<br />\n不如戒煙啦<br />\n你食煙，有冇諗過影響到人<br />\n唔係話你啲二手煙會令人致癌<br />\n我講緊你會影響屋企人啊，屋企人好擔心你嘅健康<br />\n我爺爺食煙食得好勁<br />\n到老身體機能退化得好快<br />\n心瓣鈣化，腎功能有事，肺功能好差<br />\n呼吸，大小二便都要靠人幫忙<br />\n做孫嘅好自責<br />\n點解唔出兩句聲勸佢唔好食<br />\n點解唔狠心啲收起啲煙<br />\n爺爺入左院一個月啦<br />\n情況未見好轉<br />\n每次探佢見到佢話好辛苦<br />\n我其實都辛苦<br />\n我做細嘅唔想見到屋企人受苦<br />\n亦好怕佢會出唔返黎<br />\n你愛屋企人嘅話<br />\n不如開始戒煙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b78158bdee662c3edb3d90cb773bec8c340560bf","tid":163900,"uid":61518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:24:31.000Z","msg":"我都好憎人食煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有啲仲要一路食一路行<br />\n喺後面硬食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcb4c701e9eaa6af5770c1fcf917dce14c791f6d","tid":163900,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:27:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>煙價成日加<br />\n食煙既地方越黎越少（茶餐廳都唔比食）<br />\n無地方食，咁有時影響到人好正常，又比人啤<br />\n有無平權撚可以幫下我地煙民發聲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地煙民一直被歧視,打壓"},{"pid":"1a1e47af7fc050d9653548890b3080e71e377577","tid":163900,"uid":61832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:27:53.000Z","msg":"我自己有食<br />\n但我永遠只會係吸煙區食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24b42a847c1f7c081bc5cdcbaccdbdb1950f9568","tid":163900,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:28:28.000Z","msg":"有人搵支槍指住你要食咩<br />\n<br />\nbtw多謝你地交咁多稅"},{"pid":"c7e281fbefa8c745693f08aa6dc08e6791b1c6a6","tid":163900,"uid":63350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:29:22.000Z","msg":"煙剷影響到人死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0cf31639440b715682a6bb4341d6c4995a0359d","tid":163900,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:29:28.000Z","msg":"假膠都咁多人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\"